test.sql: SELECT FLOOR([t0].[__measure__0] / 475) AS [LOD - Fixed - 1 (bin)], SUM([Staples].[Sales Total]) AS [sum:Sales Total:ok] FROM [dbo].[Staples] [Staples] INNER JOIN ( SELECT [Staples].[Market Segment] AS [Market Segment], SUM([Staples].[Product Base Margin]) AS [__measure__0] FROM [dbo].[Staples] [Staples] GROUP BY [Staples].[Market Segment] ) [t0] ON (([Staples].[Market Segment] = [t0].[Market Segment]) OR (([Staples].[Market Segment] IS NULL) AND ([t0].[Market Segment] IS NULL))) GROUP BY FLOOR([t0].[__measure__0] / 475)
